Born and raised in the historical city of Istanbul, the Barcelona-residing luminary&nbsp;**ELIF**, is a multi-talented producer and DJ who’s reputable for her versatility and authentic artistry.&nbsp;

Forming a unique relationship with her audience through her&nbsp;**hypnotic performances**&nbsp;and&nbsp;**irresistible**&nbsp;music, ELIF’s ability to push conventional sounds has solidified her acclaimed status, becoming one of the most sought-after artists in electronic music!

Now the owner of a growing record label named&nbsp;**Marginalia**, a home for emerging talent. ELIF is constantly evolving and perfecting her craft; her determination to succeed speaks for itself.&nbsp;

Accumulating&nbsp;**millions of streams**&nbsp;across DSP’s and building an ever-growing fanbase, you may be familiar with fan favourites ‘**Bamboo Forest’, ‘Release The Beast – ELIF Remix’, ‘Let Go’, and ‘Moonspell’.**&nbsp;

Playing a variety of shows across the globe, alongside further support from B**BC Radio 1 [Pete Tong], KISS FM [Ben Malone], MixMag Asia, LA Weekly, Techno Der Visionaere, CORE Radio**, and many more, this isn’t the last you’ll hear from the trailblazer.
